arameters give rise to hardware QA\ndistributions closely approximating classical Boltzmann distributions that are\nhard to train with CD/PCD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2016 19:15:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-15"}
