\nNRAO user base do not allow us to investigate the important question of the\ndependence on the gender-related trends of the seniority of the principal\ninvestigators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2016 11:31:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-16"}
